---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Historic Trends - USCIS Stats" description="Compare historic trends of case processing volumes across various forms.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-4">Historic Trends</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-500">Aggregate insights and volume trends across major USCIS form types.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-200 p-12 text-center">
      <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-neutral-300 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
      </svg>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Advanced Analytics Coming Soon</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-500">We are currently aggregating historical dataset files to build cross-form comparative charts. Check back soon for detailed backlog trend analysis.</p>
      
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/uscis-stats" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-neutral-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
          Return to Hub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
